    <main>
      <div class="block small centered">
        <h1>An outliner without the hierarchy.</h1>

        <p>Outliners are great for taking notes, but they have one problem:
        people don't think in lists. Thinktool looks like an outliner but lets
        you freely connect related items without worrying about how to organize
        them in a hierarchy.</p>
      </div>

